SPL “KYC-PASS” NFT  
- Mint 10 000 NFTs (0.1 SOL each) that act as license keys.  
- The SDK `update_kyc_level` instruction checks:  
  `assert!(kyc_pass_mint.owner == signer || kyc_pass_mint.delegate == signer)`  
- This lets you charge per wallet rather than per call (cheaper UX).

Subscription plugin  
- Add an `expires_at: i64` field to `KycAccount`.  
- Create `extend_subscription(kyc_pass_mint, months)` instruction that transfers USDC to your treasury PDA.  
- Emit `SubscriptionExtended` event for off-chain invoicing.